messages.content: What does Auto prompt by LLM and LLM-Vision do?
Auto prompt by LLM and LLM-Vision triggers more details out inside the model for SD-WEB-UI and ComfyUI.
What is the purpose of the LINE-Notify extension?
The LINE-Notify extension allows messages from SD-WEB-UI and ComfyUI to be sent to LINE Notify messages.
What does Auto msg to ur mobile extension do?
The Auto msg to ur mobile extension sends SD-image-generated results and the required link to messages LM Bot and LLM-Vision Bot in real-time.
What is the purpose of the Time UI extension?
The Time UI extension sends SD-image-generated results every 10, 60, or 120 seconds and each result image generated by SD.
How does the SD-WEB-UI & ComfyUI extension work?
The SD-WEB-UI & ComfyUI extension creates an SD-Web UI Extension by adding exchange auto-messaging
What does RX-only and RX+TX refer to?
RX-only (Receive only) allows the user to receive messages from SD-WEB-UI and ComfyUI via LINE Notify. RX+TX (Receive & Transmit) allows the user to both receive and transmit messages.
What does the ComfyUI Extension do?
The ComfyUI Extension allows the user to add custom nodes and plugins to ComfyUI that extend its functionality.
What is the signal source of the SD-WEB-UI & ComfyUI extension?
The SD-WEB-UI & ComfyUI extension uses SD for the signal source.
How does the ComfyUI Extension work?
The ComfyUI Extension is a set of custom nodes and plugins that allow for the extension of ComfyUI's functionality.
What is the main purpose of the SD-WEB-UI & ComfyUI extension?

The main purpose of the SD-WEB-UI & ComfyUI extension is to enable auto messaging between SD-WEB-UI, ComfyUI and multiple platforms (like LINE, Telegram, Discord) for remote control/monitoring and receiving SD-generated results.
